is beginning.

00:44:01.700 --> 00:44:05.630 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: And everybody-- all
the intelligent people on Earth

00:44:05.630 --> 00:44:09.340 align:middle line:84%
all are reaching the same
conclusions about reality all

00:44:09.340 --> 00:44:11.630 align:middle line:84%
at the same time
because of the internet.

00:44:11.630 --> 00:44:14.140 align:middle line:84%
And that is going
to push it over.

00:44:14.140 --> 00:44:15.390 align:middle line:90%
That's the turning point.

00:44:15.390 --> 00:44:18.720 align:middle line:84%
I call it the rebellion
of the intelligent.

00:44:18.720 --> 00:44:22.470 align:middle line:84%
It's not going to be 40%
or 80% of the people.

00:44:22.470 --> 00:44:24.410 align:middle line:84%
It's going to be
about 5%, and they're

00:44:24.410 --> 00:44:26.240 align:middle line:90%
going to be the smartest people.

00:44:26.240 --> 00:44:28.280 align:middle line:84%
And they're on the internet
right now every day,

00:44:28.280 --> 00:44:32.120 align:middle line:84%
and they're going, damn,
I'm getting mad about this.

00:44:32.120 --> 00:44:35.120 align:middle line:84%
I'm figuring this out, and
it's not making me happy.

00:44:35.120 --> 00:44:35.930 align:middle line:90%
And you know what?

00:44:35.930 --> 00:44:38.010 align:middle line:84%
I'm realizing there's a
whole lot of other people

00:44:38.010 --> 00:44:39.830 align:middle line:84%
that are just like
me figuring it out,

00:44:39.830 --> 00:44:41.230 align:middle line:90%
and they're not very happy.

00:44:41.230 --> 00:44:44.220 align:middle line:84%
And then we, the leading
edge of this group,

00:44:44.220 --> 00:44:48.280 align:middle line:84%
are going to say
enough's enough.

00:44:48.280 --> 00:44:50.980 align:middle line:84%
And we will have a collective
wisdom at that point

00:44:50.980 --> 00:44:55.040 align:middle line:84%
where we will say, listen,
centralized power is not

00:44:55.040 --> 00:44:56.360 align:middle line:90%
a smart move.

00:44:56.360 --> 00:44:58.310 align:middle line:84%
Dropping depleted
uranium on children

00:44:58.310 --> 00:45:00.370 align:middle line:90%
is not really very wise.

00:45:00.370 --> 00:45:03.570 align:middle line:84%
Having centralized
banking is stupid.

00:45:03.570 --> 00:45:07.264 align:middle line:84%
Having GMOs on all these
things is not smart.

00:45:07.264 --> 00:45:09.680 align:middle line:84%
And we're reaching all these
conclusions at the same time.

00:45:09.680 --> 00:45:11.370 align:middle line:84%
The corporate world
is freaking out.

00:45:11.370 --> 00:45:15.780 align:middle line:84%
They stopped Prop 37 by dropping
almost $50 million into it.

00:45:15.780 --> 00:45:17.095 align:middle line:90%
That means we're winning.

00:45:17.095 --> 00:45:19.220 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Explain Prop 37
for those who don't know.

00:45:19.220 --> 00:45:21.690 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: Prop 37 is
the anti-GMO labeling law.

00:45:21.690 --> 00:45:23.480 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't saying outlawing GMOs.

00:45:23.480 --> 00:45:25.820 align:middle line:84%
It was merely saying that
they should be on a label.

00:45:25.820 --> 00:45:26.080 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:45:26.080 --> 00:45:26.830 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Right?

00:45:26.830 --> 00:45:29.390 align:middle line:84%
And still they spent almost
$50 million to destroy it.

00:45:29.390 --> 00:45:30.500 align:middle line:90%
That means we're winning.

00:45:30.500 --> 00:45:33.160 align:middle line:84%
That means that they have
to be reduced to corruption

00:45:33.160 --> 00:45:35.320 align:middle line:84%
and bribery in order
to get their way.

00:45:35.320 --> 00:45:38.210 align:middle line:84%
They can no longer convince
us through propaganda.

00:45:38.210 --> 00:45:40.555 align:middle line:84%
We are winning this war,
and we are going to win it.

00:45:40.555 --> 00:45:41.430 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It's true.

00:45:41.430 --> 00:45:43.013 align:middle line:84%
It seems that the
subtleties are gone,

00:45:43.013 --> 00:45:44.450 align:middle line:84%
the subtle
manipulations are gone,

00:45:44.450 --> 00:45:45.790 align:middle line:84%
and now it's
bludgeoning people--

00:45:45.790 --> 00:45:46.090 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: They are.

00:45:46.090 --> 00:45:47.240 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: --bullying
and bludgeoning.

00:45:47.240 --> 00:45:48.560 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: Yeah, like
the war with Iran.

00:45:48.560 --> 00:45:48.830 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:45:48.830 --> 00:45:49.940 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: It used
to be very subtle.

00:45:49.940 --> 00:45:50.840 align:middle line:90%
Oh, they have nuclear weapons.

00:45:50.840 --> 00:45:51.930 align:middle line:90%
Let's go get them.

00:45:51.930 --> 00:45:53.120 align:middle line:90%
Nobody buys that anymore.

00:45:53.120 --> 00:45:53.680 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:45:53.680 --> 00:45:54.340 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: We bought
that with Iraq.

00:45:54.340 --> 00:45:55.380 align:middle line:90%
It didn't work.

00:45:55.380 --> 00:45:56.830 align:middle line:84%
So now they're trying all
sorts of different things,

00:45:56.830 --> 00:45:57.670 align:middle line:90%
and none of that's working.

00:45:57.670 --> 00:45:59.250 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: No, none
of it is working.

00:45:59.250 --> 00:45:59.500 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: No.

00:45:59.500 --> 00:46:00.130 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: OK.

00:46:00.130 --> 00:46:01.000 align:middle line:90%
So.

00:46:01.000 --> 00:46:04.110 align:middle line:84%
Now, let's-- before-- I want to
get into some of the biblical

00:46:04.110 --> 00:46:07.351 align:middle line:84%
references in Revelations
and all that about this time

00:46:07.351 --> 00:46:07.850 align:middle line:90%
as well.

00:46:07.850 --> 00:46:10.800 align:middle line:84%
So let's go first
to Nostradamus.

00:46:10.800 --> 00:46:11.300 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:46:11.300 --> 00:46:12.260 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Yep.

00:46:12.260 --> 00:46:20.240 align:middle line:84%
The most famous quatrain of the
last 200 years of Nostradamus,

00:46:20.240 --> 00:46:25.880 align:middle line:84%
I think it's 4-72, and
it's-- the king of terror--

00:46:25.880 --> 00:46:28.040 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to paraphrase.

00:46:28.040 --> 00:46:30.530 align:middle line:84%
It's a quatrain, it's
a four line prophecy.

00:46:30.530 --> 00:46:36.860 align:middle line:84%
The king of terror-- In
7/1999, the king of terror

00:46:36.860 --> 00:46:40.250 align:middle line:84%
shall reign in the
skies, and war will come.

00:46:40.250 --> 00:46:46.110 align:middle line:84%
So in September, 7-- sept
is 7-- September of 1999,

00:46:46.110 --> 00:46:48.530 align:middle line:84%
we're all waiting for
this thing to happen,

00:46:48.530 --> 00:46:51.644 align:middle line:84%
and it didn't happen, because
none of Nostradamus' quatrains

00:46:51.644 --> 00:46:52.810 align:middle line:90%
are what you think they are.

00:46:52.810 --> 00:46:54.880 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Well, they were
also done in an encoded way.

00:46:54.880 --> 00:46:55.170 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Exactly.

00:46:55.170 --> 00:46:56.150 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Because this
was during the Inquisition.

00:46:56.150 --> 00:46:57.370 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: He didn't
want to get found out.

00:46:57.370 --> 00:46:57.660 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:46:57.660 --> 00:46:57.910 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: OK.

00:46:57.910 --> 00:46:59.284 align:middle line:84%
But also he's
trying to teach you

00:46:59.284 --> 00:47:00.995 align:middle line:84%
that psychic
ability is possible.

00:47:00.995 --> 00:47:01.270 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:47:01.270 --> 00:47:02.900 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: Because you don't
know the quatrain until after

00:47:02.900 --> 00:47:03.560 align:middle line:90%
it's happened.

00:47:03.560 --> 00:47:03.820 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:47:03.820 --> 00:47:04.150 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: OK?

00:47:04.150 --> 00:47:05.100 align:middle line:90%
So it came and went.

00:47:05.100 --> 00:47:06.785 align:middle line:84%
We're like,
Nostradamus was wrong.

00:47:06.785 --> 00:47:07.680 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:47:07.680 --> 00:47:08.230 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:47:08.230 --> 00:47:12.880 align:middle line:84%
So then we go up forward two
years to September, 2001,

00:47:12.880 --> 00:47:15.330 align:middle line:84%
and a king of terror
did come from the skies,

00:47:15.330 --> 00:47:16.480 align:middle line:90%
and war did come.

00:47:16.480 --> 00:47:18.230 align:middle line:90%
So was he two years off?

00:47:18.230 --> 00:47:19.670 align:middle line:90%
The answer is no.

00:47:19.670 --> 00:47:20.900 align:middle line:90%
He wasn't two years off.

00:47:20.900 --> 00:47:23.190 align:middle line:90%
He was disguising the quatrain.

00:47:23.190 --> 00:47:27.570 align:middle line:84%
So you take the
year 7/1999, right?

00:47:27.570 --> 00:47:30.350 align:middle line:84%
Invert the 1, the
9, the 9, and the 9,

00:47:30.350 --> 00:47:32.890 align:middle line:90%
and it becomes 9, 1, 1, 1.

00:47:32.890 --> 00:47:33.390 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:47:33.390 --> 00:47:35.098 align:middle line:84%
You have to do a little
bit of inversion,

00:47:35.098 --> 00:47:36.780 align:middle line:90%
but he picks the date perfectly.

00:47:36.780 --> 00:47:41.040 align:middle line:84%
9/11/2001, the king of terror
shall come from the skies,

00:47:41.040 --> 00:47:42.100 align:middle line:90%
and war will come.

00:47:42.100 --> 00:47:45.370 align:middle line:90%
That was his 2012 quatrain.

00:47:45.370 --> 00:47:47.990 align:middle line:84%
That was his warning
about this time period,

00:47:47.990 --> 00:47:51.260 align:middle line:84%
that this time period would
start with that event,

00:47:51.260 --> 00:47:54.790 align:middle line:84%
that that event was going to
cause the catastrophe that

00:47:54.790 --> 00:47:57.010 align:middle line:84%
was going to lead to
what he called the Great

00:47:57.010 --> 00:48:00.550 align:middle line:84%
Bifurcation, where the human
race splits into two, one

00:48:00.550 --> 00:48:04.380 align:middle line:84%
completely asleep, following
the owls, one completely awake,

00:48:04.380 --> 00:48:06.330 align:middle line:90%
following the roosters.

00:48:06.330 --> 00:48:09.050 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: What do you then--
since you brought it up--

00:48:09.050 --> 00:48:13.420 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't going to-- but the
notion of the split world,

00:48:13.420 --> 00:48:17.370 align:middle line:84%
the notion of the two Earths--
this is something that Dolores

00:48:17.370 --> 00:48:19.620 align:middle line:84%
Cannon has gotten into
quite a bit in her work,

00:48:19.620 --> 00:48:23.760 align:middle line:84%
and in the 1980s a certain
one of esoteric circles I was

00:48:23.760 --> 00:48:27.080 align:middle line:84%
associated with at that time--
that was something that came up

00:48:27.080 --> 00:48:27.960 align:middle line:90%
then 30 years ago--

00:48:27.960 --> 00:48:28.835 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Oh, yeah.

00:48:28.835 --> 00:48:32.590 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: --which was already
people are beginning to migrate

00:48:32.590 --> 00:48:34.440 align:middle line:84%
to one world or the
other and that--

00:48:34.440 --> 00:48:36.670 align:middle line:84%
and this is important
to note in that--

00:48:36.670 --> 00:48:38.329 align:middle line:84%
that another world
has been created.

00:48:38.329 --> 00:48:39.120 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: It has.

00:48:39.120 --> 00:48:42.140 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: We don't all have to
incarnate to the same planet.

00:48:42.140 --> 00:48:43.970 align:middle line:84%
And the other world
has very carefully

00:48:43.970 --> 00:48:47.480 align:middle line:84%
been created for this period
of time in which, as you say,

00:48:47.480 --> 00:48:52.710 align:middle line:84%
this species would go through
kind of a consciousness split.

00:48:52.710 --> 00:48:56.000 align:middle line:84%
And what was told to me
30 years ago about that

00:48:56.000 --> 00:48:58.690 align:middle line:84%
is not to look on
that as a bad thing.

00:48:58.690 --> 00:49:01.800 align:middle line:84%
It was simply a time-- It's
as though you're taking people

00:49:01.800 --> 00:49:04.192 align:middle line:84%
that are in a classroom
with one level of knowledge

00:49:04.192 --> 00:49:05.900 align:middle line:84%
and another level of
knowledge and you're

00:49:05.900 --> 00:49:08.739 align:middle line:84%
making two classrooms, and
there's no punishment in that.

00:49:08.739 --> 00:49:09.780 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: That's right.

00:49:09.780 --> 00:49:11.405 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: There's
grace in everything.

00:49:11.405 --> 00:49:13.510 align:middle line:84%
There's a chance to
continue learning

00:49:13.510 --> 00:49:14.652 align:middle line:90%
what you need to learn.

00:49:14.652 --> 00:49:15.360 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Yeah.

00:49:15.360 --> 00:49:18.250 align:middle line:84%
The 12th graders have to be
tolerant of the 2nd graders.

00:49:18.250 --> 00:49:19.251 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: That's right.

00:49:19.251 --> 00:49:21.166 align:middle line:84%
>> WEIDNER: Because
they're not really stupid;

00:49:21.166 --> 00:49:22.240 align:middle line:90%
they just don't know.

00:49:22.240 --> 00:49:23.240 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: That's right.

00:49:23.240 --> 00:49:24.782 align:middle line:84%
Ignorance is simply
just to not know.

00:49:24.782 --> 00:49:25.490 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Yeah.

00:49:25.490 --> 00:49:28.130 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's up to us, the
rebellion of the intelligent,

00:49:28.130 --> 00:49:30.070 align:middle line:84%
the intelligent people
who are beginning

00:49:30.070 --> 00:49:33.300 align:middle line:84%
to figure all this out, to be
extremely tolerant and patient

00:49:33.300 --> 00:49:35.520 align:middle line:84%
with those people
who don't understand.

00:49:35.520 --> 00:49:38.900 align:middle line:84%
So when you're going home
over the holidays or whatever,

00:49:38.900 --> 00:49:41.900 align:middle line:84%
just because your relatives
are dumb as a bag of rocks,

00:49:41.900 --> 00:49:45.124 align:middle line:84%
you have to just
slowly help them along.

00:49:45.124 --> 00:49:47.040 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I want to say
something about that.

00:49:47.040 --> 00:49:49.860 align:middle line:84%
I got in this conversation
recently about someone

00:49:49.860 --> 00:49:54.340 align:middle line:84%
near and dear, and she appears
to not be as, certainly,

00:49:54.340 --> 00:49:57.140 align:middle line:84%
well-educated on
a lot of things.

00:49:57.140 --> 00:50:02.160 align:middle line:84%
But what this person
has is our holy grail.

00:50:02.160 --> 00:50:05.110 align:middle line:84%
She has no judgment and
love and compassion.

00:50:05.110 --> 00:50:06.894 align:middle line:84%
She has one of the
most pristine hearts.

00:50:06.894 --> 00:50:07.560 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Yep.

00:50:07.560 --> 00:50:09.240 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Everybody makes
fun of her for having little

00:50:09.240 --> 00:50:10.120 align:middle line:90%
knowledge.

00:50:10.120 --> 00:50:13.110 align:middle line:84%
And I look at that and
say, hold on a minute.

00:50:13.110 --> 00:50:15.540 align:middle line:84%
The raising of the
frequencies has

00:50:15.540 --> 00:50:18.630 align:middle line:84%
to do very much with what's
happening on a frequency

00:50:18.630 --> 00:50:20.320 align:middle line:90%
heart-generated level.

00:50:20.320 --> 00:50:22.980 align:middle line:90%
She has that in spades.

00:50:22.980 --> 00:50:25.330 align:middle line:84%
If she never learned
a thing about 2012

00:50:25.330 --> 00:50:27.380 align:middle line:84%
or any of this stuff
we do here at Gaiam,

00:50:27.380 --> 00:50:28.770 align:middle line:90%
she's already ahead of most.

00:50:28.770 --> 00:50:29.170 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Oh, I know.

00:50:29.170 --> 00:50:30.003 align:middle line:90%
I get so frustrated.

00:50:30.003 --> 00:50:32.950 align:middle line:84%
I'll meet somebody who
will be channelling,

00:50:32.950 --> 00:50:35.120 align:middle line:84%
and they'll know
absolutely nothing.

00:50:35.120 --> 00:50:38.040 align:middle line:84%
Yet their channeling is
absolutely perfect for what

00:50:38.040 --> 00:50:40.580 align:middle line:84%
30 years of my scholarly
research has found.

00:50:40.580 --> 00:50:43.050 align:middle line:84%
I'm like, well, why
didn't I just sit

00:50:43.050 --> 00:50:45.780 align:middle line:84%
down in the lotus
position 30 years

00:50:45.780 --> 00:50:47.340 align:middle line:84%
ago and just start
channeling, and I

00:50:47.340 --> 00:50:49.900 align:middle line:84%
wouldn't have to read the
10,000 books that I read?

00:50:49.900 --> 00:50:51.515 align:middle line:90%
But everybody has a different--

00:50:51.515 --> 00:50:52.410 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It
comes down to that.

00:50:52.410 --> 00:50:52.620 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: --way, yeah.

00:50:52.620 --> 00:50:53.375 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: It's great
to be brilliant.

00:50:53.375 --> 00:50:54.660 align:middle line:90%
It's great to have a great mind.

00:50:54.660 --> 00:50:56.118 align:middle line:84%
But in the end,
the only thing that

00:50:56.118 --> 00:50:58.960 align:middle line:84%
takes you through a transition
into a higher frequency

00:50:58.960 --> 00:51:01.350 align:middle line:84%
is being of a higher frequency,
which always comes back

00:51:01.350 --> 00:51:02.492 align:middle line:90%
to love and nonjudgment.

00:51:02.492 --> 00:51:03.825 align:middle line:90%
And that gets us to Revelations.

00:51:03.825 --> 00:51:04.560 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Yep.

00:51:04.560 --> 00:51:04.800 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: OK.

00:51:04.800 --> 00:51:06.425 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about
Revelations, and we'll

00:51:06.425 --> 00:51:08.050 align:middle line:84%
bring a little of
Rocco Errico into it.

00:51:08.050 --> 00:51:08.758 align:middle line:90%
>> WEIDNER: Yeah.

00:51:08.758 --> 00:51:10.280 align:middle line:84%
What's interesting
about Revelations

00:51:10.280 --> 00:51:12.130 align:middle line:84%
is what most people
don't realize

00:51:12.130 --> 00:51:14.390 align:middle line:84%
is that the Book of
Revelation was not

00:51:14.390 --> 00:51:16.110 align:middle line:90%
written by John of Patmos.

00:51:16.110 --> 00:51:19.220 align:middle line:84%
It was a best-seller, believe
it or not, at that time,

00:51:19.220 --> 00:51:21.610 align:middle line:84%
and it was written by
Isis the Prophetess.

00:51:21.610 --> 00:51:26.270 align:middle line:84%
It was written 500 years before
John of Patmos even existed.

00:51:26.270 --> 00:51:28.090 align:middle line:90%
500 BC it was written.

00:51:28.090 --> 00:51:31.160 align:middle line:84%
And it was a prophecy
for the future written

00:51:31.160 --> 00:51:33.840 align:middle line:84%
by this prophet,
this Egyptian woman,

00:51:33.840 --> 00:51:37.400 align:middle line:84%
and it was called the
Revelation of Isis and Osiris.

00:51:37.400 --> 00:51:40.990 align:middle line:84%
And if you read Revelation,
the woman on the moon,

00:51:40.990 --> 00:51:44.311 align:middle line:84%
the crescent moon and all
the symbols, that's all Isis.

00:51:44.311 --> 00:51:45.310 align:middle line:90%
He's talking about Isis.

00:51:45.310 --> 00:51:48.040 align:middle line:84%
And the Catholic Church
has these treatises saying,

00:51:48.040 --> 00:51:49.364 align:middle line:90%
what is he talking about?

